trans-unit.source: Use the `CallTarget` element in your project file to create and execute this task.
trans-unit.target: Bruk av `CallTarget` elementet i prosjektfilen til å opprette og kjøre denne oppgaven.

trans-unit.source: For usage and parameter information, see [CallTarget Task](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: For bruk og parametere informasjon, se [CallTarget oppgaven](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="Microsoft.Build.Tasks.CallTarget"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="Microsoft.Build.Tasks.CallTarget"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: Instructs the [!INCLUDE[vstecmsbuild](~/add/includes/vstecmsbuild-md.md)] engine to build one or more targets in the current project.
trans-unit.target: Angir at det [!INCLUDE[vstecmsbuild](~/add/includes/vstecmsbuild-md.md)] motoren å bygge en eller flere mål i gjeldende prosjekt.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if all targets built successfully; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Hvis alle mål for bygging vellykket; Ellers <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a Boolean value that indicates whether the [!INCLUDE[vstecmsbuild](~/add/includes/vstecmsbuild-md.md)] engine is called once per target (<xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>) or the [!INCLUDE[vstecmsbuild](~/add/includes/vstecmsbuild-md.md)] engine is called once to build all targets (<xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>).
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir en boolsk verdi som angir om den [!INCLUDE[vstecmsbuild](~/add/includes/vstecmsbuild-md.md)] motoren kalles én gang per mål (<xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>) eller [!INCLUDE[vstecmsbuild](~/add/includes/vstecmsbuild-md.md)] motoren kalles én gang for å bygge alle mål (<xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>).

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the [!INCLUDE[vstecmsbuild](~/add/includes/vstecmsbuild-md.md)] engine is called once per target; <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref> if the [!INCLUDE[vstecmsbuild](~/add/includes/vstecmsbuild-md.md)] engine is called once to build all targets.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Hvis den [!INCLUDE[vstecmsbuild](~/add/includes/vstecmsbuild-md.md)] motoren kalles én gang per måltype. <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref> hvis den [!INCLUDE[vstecmsbuild](~/add/includes/vstecmsbuild-md.md)] motoren kalles én gang for å bygge alle mål.

trans-unit.source: Gets the outputs of all built targets.
trans-unit.target: Henter utdataene for alle innebygde mål.

trans-unit.source: The outputs of all built targets.
Gets or sets the target or targets to build.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir mål eller mål å bygge.

trans-unit.source: The target or targets to build.
Gets or sets a Boolean value that indicates whether the MSBuild engine will return the built targets from the cache.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir en boolsk verdi som angir om MSBuild-motoren tilbakestiller innebygd målene fra hurtigbufferen.

trans-unit.source: The scope of built targets in the cash is (ProjectFileName, GlobalProperties)[TargetNames] as a list of build items.
trans-unit.target: Den innebygde mål i kontanter er (ProjectFileName GlobalProperties) [TargetNames] som en liste med elementer som kompilering.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the MSBuild engine will return the built targets from the cache; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Hvis MSBuild-motoren skal returnere innebygd målene fra hurtigbufferen; Ellers <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.
